==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Intermural
<hw>In`ter*mu"ral</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Lying between walls; inclosed by walls.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Taking place between two different institutions or
cities; <as>as, an <ex>intermural</ex> soccer match between two
schools</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intermure</ent>⟦br⟧
